msgid "Always go through the `cargo mdbook …` wrapper. Running `mdbook build` directly from `docs/book/` skips the xtask step that renders `theme/lang-switcher.js` from `locales.toml`, which fails the build with `failed to open theme/lang-switcher.js for hashing`."
