#: src/agents/anatomy.md
msgid "`Config::validate()` fails loud at startup if `model_provider` does not resolve to a configured provider entry, or if `risk_profile` does not resolve to a configured risk profile. A bad reference is caught before the agent runs, not silently ignored."
