msgid "`CostTracker::record_usage_with_agent` appends one `CostRecord` per priced response to `<workspace>/state/costs.jsonl`, one JSON object per line. The file is read on startup to seed `daily_records()` so the dashboard's per-agent rollup survives restarts."
